Package: com.zeshan.phoneaura
Name: PhoneAura
Version: 0.2.1
Architecture: iphoneos-arm64e
Description: Navigation safety release for the iOS 16 Phone app. Restores Apple's real tab controller and overlays a compact interactive glass dock without replacing the keypad, blocking content, or trapping the user on one screen.
